    public static enum MergedFOV.MergeType
extends java.lang.Enum<MergedFOV.MergeType>
    Used when constructing a MergedFOV to indicate what kind of merge should be performed.

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      AND
      The weight will be used to average out all light maps, but if any light map shows a cell to have no light then it will be marked as unlit.
      MAXIMUM
      The maximum light from the light maps will be used.
      MINIMUM
      The minimum light from the light maps will be used.
      WEIGHTED_AVERAGE
      The weight will be used to average out all light maps.
